  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亲爱的小怪物们：今日游戏上线，玩家数量超乎我们的预期，所以服务器出现不稳定的情况，我们正在紧急修复这个问题，建议玩家们在此期间先不要登录游玩多人版游戏，后期我们会进行服务器开放通知，谢谢您的配合！</h2><br><br><strong>加入《人中怪物多人版》官方玩家群：339025561，了解更多！<br>欢迎关注官方微博：@九头龙工作室</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/644da7b7cb3cd7d1791344ae21fdd32f.avif?t=1713931338\" width=562 height=242 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本作仍处于开发期，建议玩家在调试完整之后再进行购买。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本版本为内测版本，为了配合测试，我们设置了一个错误返回功能，以及为小鸟游梦角色设定了特殊等级进行相关测试，最终版本我们会关闭与修改这两项内容。<br>在内测阶段结束后，我们会将游戏进行删档，同时会为提前购买的玩家赠送20张抽奖券。如果小怪物们在游戏中发现任何问题，或者有一些宝贵的意见或建议，也欢迎向我们反馈~</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><strong>《人中怪物多人版》是由九头龙工作室独立研发的一款恐怖策略休闲类游戏。您将和您的几位同伴在一栋神秘的洋馆同时醒来，大家需要一起探索洋馆中的秘密，完成洋馆主人发布的任务，通过洋馆中的各个线索碎片，推理分析出正确的传送门位置，从而逃出这栋恐怖的洋馆。<br>但需要注意的是，在大家苏醒之前，已经有1-2名玩家被可怕的怪物所替代，他们隐藏在玩家之中，目的是杀光所有人，所以怪物们通常会通过谎言欺骗他人为自己争取更多的杀戮时间。<br>对于人类来说，逃出洋馆的方法除了找到传送门外，指认出我们之中的怪物是更加快捷的途径。所以在每轮任务结束后的发言讨论过程中，告知大家你找到的一切有关怪物和能够自证清白的线索。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务</h2><strong>根据洋馆主人发布的任务，完成各种房间内的小游戏。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/7f3ec57c7861e80b86856e1dd95c4c57.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=629 height=367 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/7f3ec57c7861e80b86856e1dd95c4c57.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/fed05e8302c7e2d626683b56f9e70d21.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=634 height=451 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/fed05e8302c7e2d626683b56f9e70d21.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >线索</h2><strong>探索房间，寻找洋馆中的日记碎片，根据碎片上的线索，推理出正确的传送门位置。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/b22028c6d1e010be37d3a032d45601a9.avif?t=1713931338\" width=579 height=651 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/d10e97885e8e6ade46494dad2098ac8c.avif?t=1713931338\" width=579 height=651 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现</h2><strong>发现房间中诡异的机关和线索。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/b7cc874b07f4977751eee369b093f853.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=573 height=445 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/b7cc874b07f4977751eee369b093f853.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/e2a3940cd7c5c1c385398a809acb8c4a.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=406 height=341 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/e2a3940cd7c5c1c385398a809acb8c4a.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >突发</h2><strong>除了突然喷涌的血迹外，洋馆内还住着两个十分“可爱”的小动物，不过它们比较喜欢恶作剧，如果你突然见到它们可不要紧张的大叫哟！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/0817e7805cb3ccf384872885eb875918.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=568 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/0817e7805cb3ccf384872885eb875918.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >讨论</h2><strong>通过语音交流讨论，分析细节并自证清白。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/7a78314c84a2a86d454bdd7f4c767233.avif?t=1713931338\" width=640 height=399 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀戮</h2><strong>怪物玩家不要忘记你最重要的任务，试着在不为人知的时候杀掉其他人。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/7d8614546e317675ef130c0aaa1f250d.poster.avif?t=1713931338\" width=640 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746110/extras/7d8614546e317675ef130c0aaa1f250d.webm?t=1713931338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在游戏中解锁各个人物的剧情，让我们开始感受推理的快乐吧！</strong>",
